sqlQuery: SELECT customer_address.ca_country, SUM(web_sales.ws_net_profit + customer_demographics.cd_dep_college_count) as agg_0, AVG(web_returns.wr_reason_sk) as agg_1, MAX(date_dim.d_year) as agg_2 FROM web_page JOIN web_returns ON web_page.wp_web_page_sk = web_returns.wr_web_page_sk JOIN time_dim ON web_returns.wr_returned_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk JOIN customer_address ON web_returns.wr_returning_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN reason ON web_returns.wr_reason_sk = reason.r_reason_sk JOIN date_dim ON web_page.wp_access_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk JOIN web_sales ON time_dim.t_time_sk = web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON date_dim.d_date_sk = catalog_sales.cs_sold_date_sk JOIN web_site ON date_dim.d_date_sk = web_site.web_close_date_sk JOIN customer_demographics ON catalog_sales.cs_bill_cdemo_sk = customer_demographics.cd_demo_sk  WHERE date_dim.d_holiday = 'N' AND customer_demographics.cd_gender IN ('M', 'F') AND web_returns.wr_returned_date_sk <= 2452209.571812627 AND reason.r_reason_desc IN ('Found a better price in a store', 'Not the product that was ordred', 'reason 31', 'Lost my job', 'reason 35', 'Does not work with a product that I have', 'Parts missing', 'reason 33', 'reason 24', 'duplicate purchase') AND time_dim.t_time_sk <= 77055.30161326617 AND web_page.wp_web_page_sk >= 3.634050457349878 AND time_dim.t_meal_time IN ('breakfast') AND customer_address.ca_suite_number LIKE '%270%' AND customer_demographics.cd_marital_status IN ('U', 'W') AND reason.r_reason_desc IN ('Did not fit', 'Package was damaged', 'Does not work with a product that I have', 'Not working any more') AND web_page.wp_url = 'http://www.foo.com' AND web_page.wp_creation_date_sk >= 2450815.0 GROUP BY customer_address.ca_country HAVING SUM(web_sales.ws_net_profit + customer_demographics.cd_dep_college_count) != -257.64897560968825 ORDER BY customer_address.ca_country LIMIT 1000;

SELECT customer_address.ca_zip, AVG(store_sales.ss_wholesale_cost) as agg_0 FROM customer_address JOIN store_sales ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = store_sales.ss_addr_sk JOIN item ON store_sales.ss_item_sk = item.i_item_sk JOIN store_returns ON item.i_item_sk = store_returns.sr_item_sk JOIN inventory ON item.i_item_sk = inventory.inv_item_sk JOIN warehouse ON inventory.inv_warehouse_sk = warehouse.w_warehouse_sk JOIN customer ON store_returns.sr_customer_sk = customer.c_customer_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = catalog_returns.cr_returning_addr_sk JOIN web_returns ON item.i_item_sk = web_returns.wr_item_sk JOIN web_sales ON warehouse.w_warehouse_sk = web_sales.ws_warehouse_sk JOIN time_dim ON web_sales.ws_sold_time_sk = time_dim.t_time_sk  WHERE inventory.inv_date_sk <= 2452192.879405851 AND inventory.inv_item_sk <= 6343.483271794472 AND time_dim.t_sub_shift LIKE '%morning%' AND warehouse.w_city NOT LIKE '%Fa%irview%' AND inventory.inv_quantity_on_hand >= 425.58417060421505 AND (warehouse.w_warehouse_sk <= 2.3263760078701154 OR (warehouse.w_warehouse_id != 'AAAAAAAADAAAAAAA' AND warehouse.w_warehouse_sk <= 2.0678617742913645)) AND web_sales.ws_net_paid_inc_ship_tax >= 4949.939446498163 AND customer.c_last_name IS NOT NULL AND web_sales.ws_bill_addr_sk <= 35377.66885778185 AND web_sales.ws_warehouse_sk >= 1.8223204921972083 GROUP BY customer_address.ca_zip ORDER BY customer_address.ca_zip;

SELECT promotion.p_channel_radio, warehouse.w_warehouse_id, customer_address.ca_location_type, SUM(web_sales.ws_bill_cdemo_sk + catalog_sales.cs_net_paid) as agg_0 FROM item JOIN store_sales ON item.i_item_sk = store_sales.ss_item_sk JOIN catalog_sales ON item.i_item_sk = catalog_sales.cs_item_sk JOIN customer_address ON catalog_sales.cs_ship_addr_sk = customer_address.ca_address_sk JOIN web_sales ON customer_address.ca_address_sk = web_sales.ws_ship_addr_sk JOIN household_demographics ON store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk JOIN promotion ON catalog_sales.cs_promo_sk = promotion.p_promo_sk JOIN inventory ON item.i_item_sk = inventory.inv_item_sk JOIN catalog_returns ON item.i_item_sk = catalog_returns.cr_item_sk JOIN warehouse ON inventory.inv_warehouse_sk = warehouse.w_warehouse_sk JOIN customer ON household_demographics.hd_demo_sk = customer.c_current_hdemo_sk  WHERE item.i_category_id <= 4.650085117042099 AND catalog_returns.cr_item_sk <= 10578.79246910237 AND item.i_category IN ('Sports', 'Jewelry', 'Women') AND catalog_returns.cr_returning_cdemo_sk >= 288982.89590349235 AND promotion.p_channel_email IS NOT NULL AND customer.c_current_hdemo_sk <= 5118.153243233474 AND household_demographics.hd_dep_count >= 8.10107694406769 AND inventory.inv_item_sk <= 2325.373137506761 AND (store_sales.ss_addr_sk <= 44974.275688292415 OR store_sales.ss_item_sk >= 9349.647636467373) AND (customer_address.ca_state LIKE '%CA%' OR customer_address.ca_state IS NOT NULL OR customer_address.ca_state NOT LIKE '%CO%') AND (promotion.p_channel_details LIKE '%o%nly%' OR promotion.p_channel_details IN ('Final workers resign. Now nuclear accounts get r', 'Over stupid guidelines know live projects. Still common num', 'Public, running ladies l', 'Concepts might live of cours', 'Available, blue hours explo', 'Inadequate christians can try possible, pal') OR promotion.p_channel_details IN ('Others deal both companies. Separ', 'Deaf, tall members create as well confe', 'Able patients will lend as. Southern components must com', 'Earlier traditional groups', 'Increases could not buy socia', 'Safe women change old, ', 'Briefly old records must not find precious instr')) AND household_demographics.hd_buy_potential != '>10000' AND web_sales.ws_net_profit >= -582.0753752439728 AND item.i_units IN ('Pound', 'Dram', 'Pallet', 'Cup') AND promotion.p_channel_catalog = 'N' AND catalog_returns.cr_return_amount >= 2650.194403697188 AND promotion.p_channel_radio != 'N' AND (customer_address.ca_city != 'Royal' OR customer_address.ca_suite_number != 'Suite 140') GROUP BY promotion.p_channel_radio, warehouse.w_warehouse_id, customer_address.ca_location_type ORDER BY promotion.p_channel_radio, warehouse.w_warehouse_id, customer_address.ca_location_type;
